OL,3,CNHS trust 'fully accepts' watchdog
OL,4,Crecommendations after killer care
OL,6,FThe chief executive of a trust
OL,7,Finvolved in the care of a paranoid
OL,8,Fschizophrenic who killed three people
OL,9,Fin Nottingham says he "fully accepts"
OL,10,Frecommendations from the health
OL,11,Fwatchdog.
OL,13,FMental health services provided at
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust came under scrutiny
OL,16,Fin a report by the Care Quality
OL,17,FCommission (CQC) released in August,
OL,18,Fwhich said the killer's risk was "not
OL,19,Fmanaged well".
