OL,3,CNHS trust 'fully accepts' watchdog
OL,4,Crecommendations after killer care
OL,6,FValdo Calocane, who killed Nottingham
OL,7,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,8,FO'Malley-Kumar and school caretaker
OL,9,FIan Coates on June 13 last year, was
OL,10,Funder the care of the trust between
OL,11,FMay 2020 and September 2022.
OL,13,FChief executive of the trust, Ifti
OL,14,FMajid, said on Thursday at the trust's
OL,15,Fpublic board of directors meeting at
OL,16,FHighbury Hospital, Nottinghamshire,
OL,17,Fthat he "understands" where it "missed
OL,18,Fopportunities" in the areas outlined
OL,19,Fin the report.
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@UO]yD@`OUzD@NO]
