OL,3,CNHS trust 'fully accepts' watchdog
OL,4,Crecommendations after killer care
OL,6,F"We've accepted all the
OL,7,Frecommendations, and we have moved
OL,8,Fthose recommendations into the
OL,9,Fintegrated improvement plan already."
OL,11,FThe watchdog has suggested that the
OL,12,Ftrust should regularly review
OL,13,Ftreatment plans for paranoid
OL,14,Fschizophrenics, ensure staff engage
OL,15,Fwith patients' families, have a robust
OL,16,Fdischarge policy, and have clinical
OL,17,Fsupervisions of decisions to detain
OL,18,Fpeople under the Mental Health Act.
