OL,6,FIn the board meeting documents shared
OL,7,Fpublicly, Mr Majid wrote: "It goes
OL,8,Fwithout saying that I have offered my
OL,9,Fsincere apologies to the families of
OL,10,FGrace, Ian and Barnaby who lost their
OL,11,Flives; and to Wayne, Sharon and
OL,12,FMarcion who were seriously injured,
OL,13,Ffor any missed opportunities in our
OL,14,Fcare, treatment, and interactions with
OL,15,FValdo Calocane.
OL,26,@oD@[OU
