OL,4,Crecommendations after killer care
OL,6,F"As we formally accept these
OL,7,Frecommendations and the findings in
OL,8,Fpublic today, foremost in our minds
OL,9,Fmust be the people who lost loved
OL,10,Fones, and whose lives changed
OL,11,Fpermanently following the catastrophic
OL,12,Fevents of June last year."
OL,14,FMr Majid said that the trust has
OL,15,Falready "significantly improved"
OL,16,Fprocesses and has moved the
OL,17,Frecommendations by the CQC into its
OL,18,Fintegrated improvement plan.
